# Survey Form Project

This is a simple **Survey Form** built as part of the [freeCodeCamp Responsive Web Design Certification](https://www.freecodecamp.org/).  
It was created to practice **HTML5** and **CSS3** fundamentals such as forms, inputs, labels, and responsive layouts.

